    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and perfect for someone looking for a dependable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for many more adventures with its next owner! I'd love for this car to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32900.0,
