      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey friends! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly such a great find! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in wonderful shape, just waiting for its next adventure. If you're looking for a solid ride that looks sharp and drives even better, this is definitely the one for you. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Can't wait to see who takes it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
